'''Lucasfilm Animation''' is a division of [[Lucasfilm]] that was founded in [[2003]]. It is a digital animation studio that produces Lucasfilm's animated content for films, games, and television. Lucasfilm Animation was responsible for the ''[[Star Wars: The Clone Wars]]'' 3D animated television series, in conjunction with [[Lucasfilm Animation Singapore]]. The studio also produced ''[[Star Wars Rebels]]'', the unreleased ''[[Star Wars Detours]]'' television series, ''[[Star Wars Forces of Destiny]]'', ''[[Star Wars Resistance]]'', and a variety of television series for [[Disney+]].

[[Cary Silver]] is currently the executive producer at Lucasfilm Animation.

